Package com.mediamiser.api.adapter

XmlAdapters used to serialize/deserialize types.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DateAdapter
    This adapter allows for Date objects to be marshalled/unmarshalled to and from RFC 3339 timestamps.
    LocaleAdapter
    This adapter allows for Locale objects to be marshalled/unmarshalled to and from BCP 47 tags.
